Class DaySessions

Namespace
FinSysPlatform.Domain.Market

FinSysPlatform.Domain.Market.dll

A collection of sessions Session inside a day The simplest case is the day contains a single session, for example, 09:00 - 17:00 Another well-common case is the instrument may be available across day border, for example, 00:00 - 04:00 and then 16:00-24:00 And rare cases, when an instrument is available in some small periods, for example: 00:00 - 04:00, 07:00-12:00, 13:00-15:00, 16:00-24:00
